WEBVTT

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:05.416
Today, for example,
less than a quarter of Europeans

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:10.080
trust online businesses
to protect their personal information.

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:14.320
But what if people knew

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:18.776
that they could rely
on technology companies

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:20.120
to treat them fairly?

00:13:22.280 --> 00:13:24.696
What if they knew that those companies

00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:28.320
respond to competition
by trying to do better,

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:31.680
by trying to serve consumers better,